Hi everyone, greetings from @geekskuadproject . If you're one of our current class mates you'll find 9 of this post on your timeline and here's why. The nine of us (@monicaariesta @ovitapp @nicholasvallen @purplevalen @frsindra @b_stevan @joannakrista @angelagrct @johannafebriany) are currently working on a project named #GEEKSKUADPROJECT or GSP in short which (hopefully) will soon be operational. The project was initiated last year when we did a colaboration work in anticipation of Marvel's Civil War and we found that we are all geeks on a certain level in our life. The project will cover arts (both original and fanarts) which mostly will revolve around comics and heroes. Please do support us by following our account @geekskuadproject . Your support will mean so much to each and everyone of us GSP members.
